sentences: Ma olen andnud talle kõik vajalikud dokumendid.
Ta on andnud mulle head nõuanded.
Nende on andnud meile palju abi.
context: The word 'andnud' is the past tense of the verb 'andma', which means to give or provide something. It is commonly used in Estonian language to express that someone has given or provided something to someone else.
